des:
Ask for Indian Mythology, and learn about interesting facts about Indian Mythology.

Indian Mythology is a fact skill that will provide interesting facts about Indian Mythology that you don't know. 

To start, just say "Alexa, launch Indian Mythology" or "Alexa, open Indian Mythology" to get a fact".
